==English==

===Etymology===
From [[restless]] + [[-ness]]

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-restlessness.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''restlessness'''

# The state or condition of being [[restless]]; an inability to be [[still]], [[quiet]], or [[comfortable]].
#: ''She sat and fidgeted out of '''restlessness''' as she waited.''

